[{"Code":"en","Title":"Set up webhooks","Slug":"payouts-set-up-webhooks","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"58140471-fa0d-4d9a-a6d3-078d69246584\">Learn how you can be notified of any status changes for your payouts in real-time. For the best payout experience, we highly recommend you to subscribe to our webhooks.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"863d3d45-0669-40f7-b51c-f9d602694be0\">Set up your Webhook URL</h2><p data-block-id=\"98241c76-6e0d-4e79-9470-1d60440bc8ae\"><strong>Important:</strong> You need <code>Developer</code> access to set up</p><p data-block-id=\"98241c76-6e0d-4e79-9470-1d60440bc8ae\">Follow the following instructions to start setting up your webhook URL:</p><ol data-block-id=\"2394da81-f8ea-48a3-a732-ecfb59ad4afd\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"4dc6629e-21e4-4e4e-b0a0-397138b4d103\"><p data-block-id=\"a90efd07-2694-4d9c-b788-c7acca47e724\">Log in to your Xendit Dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"566c6980-6c91-4691-81ff-6ec1e70ceb49\"><p data-block-id=\"52609f8f-1f58-4e56-8523-e94c0fa0c7eb\">Open <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#webhooks\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Webhook Settings</strong></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ed67b9c2-3c6d-44b5-8606-172514301f85\"><p data-block-id=\"5bdff958-f47c-4b8d-b67a-21cf8a809c67\">Configure your <strong>URL on each webhook event</strong> you want to subscribe</p></li><li data-block-id=\"39363386-69ef-48f5-ad6b-d4c3e8afd745\"><p data-block-id=\"056e4ed7-24d1-4a5f-a2de-6b8eb5911b44\">Click <strong>Test and Save</strong> to receive test webhooks</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"73c6a165-cf78-4dbe-b0c4-2a161011bee1\">For more information on the different webhook events that you can subscribe, refer to your corresponding payout product integration page.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"a28b1831-ed44-4f55-b125-7047e14e55ff\">Payouts and Payout Links</h3><p data-block-id=\"e5395fa7-7a18-4100-97f2-bdf4d379c69c\"><img data-block-id=\"6d70ee74-22db-4b8f-b642-b56a04482c10\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(104).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"0b976c01-dc8d-40c3-9974-319906ba3fd2\">Cross-Border Payouts</h3><blockquote data-block-id=\"55a629d3-cad8-48d8-9766-bb5522e701ab\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\" style=\"background:rgb(221, 247, 255);border-left:4px solid rgb(0, 106, 138);overflow:auto;\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"acf0fe21-b9de-44f1-a3b9-46e66263914c\">Important Note</p></div><p data-block-id=\"44cca3e6-432a-4cf8-9a29-7cbf5aeddb9e\">Only shown when you are registered as a remittance-licensed entity in Xendit</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"c3034113-8c45-43a5-afbb-4b8d1cc6fbf2\"><img data-block-id=\"19e9f308-bafd-422c-8fdf-9f3e0b0a354c\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(106).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"2b8b4329-7609-4801-859e-b52643cdbafa\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Set up webhooks","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Atur webhook","Slug":"payouts-set-up-webhooks","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mccc03yq-9in16c-634\">Pelajari cara Anda dapat menerima notifikasi tentang perubahan status untuk pembayaran Anda secara real-time. Untuk pengalaman pembayaran terbaik, kami sangat menyarankan Anda untuk berlangganan webhook kami.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mccc03yq-klbxqg-635\">Menyiapkan URL Webhook Anda</h2><p data-block-id=\"mccc03yq-o9zlmr-636\"><strong>Penting:</strong> Anda memerlukan akses <code>Developer</code></p><p data-block-id=\"mccc03yq-wq9e9j-637\">Ikuti petunjuk berikut untuk mulai menyiapkan URL webhook Anda:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mccc03yq-wcy760-638\" start=\"1\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"mccc03yq-gu1okj-639\"><p data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-flse6j-640\">Masuk ke Dasbor Xendit Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-ojs0dx-641\"><p data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-ipaomp-642\">Buka <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#webhooks\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Webhook Settings</strong></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-d5t8a0-643\"><p data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-r6f278-644\">Konfigurasikan URL Anda <strong>di setiap event webhook</strong> yang ingin Anda langgan</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-drp4df-645\"><p data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-ciqafu-646\">Klik <strong>Tesdan Simpan</strong> untuk menerima webhook pengujian</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-z6ygp6-647\">Untuk informasi selengkapnya tentang berbagai event webhook yang dapat Anda langganan, lihat halaman integrasi produk payout yang sesuai.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-s2bfw0-648\">Payoutdan Link Payout</h3><p data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-fuo1f6-649\"><img data-block-id=\"mccc03yr-nlmpxy-650\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(104).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"mccc03ys-pmbi21-651\">Cross-Border Payout</h3><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mccc03ys-a9m6y5-652\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mccc03ys-x3x8a7-653\">Catatan Penting</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mccc03ys-b6usg8-654\">Fitur ini hanya tersedia ketika Anda terdaftar sebagai entitas berlisensi remittance di Xendit</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"mccc03ys-4iwofi-655\"><img data-block-id=\"mccc03ys-da7hg5-656\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(106).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mccc03ys-4f44uw-657\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Atur webhook","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ตั้งค่า webhook","Slug":"setting-up-webhooks-1","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"58140471-fa0d-4d9a-a6d3-078d69246584\">เรียนรู้วิธีที่คุณจะได้รับการแจ้งเตือนเกี่ยวกับการเปลี่ยนแปลงสถานะสำหรับ Payouts ของคุณแบบเรียลไทม์ เพื่อประสบการณ์ Payout ที่ดีที่สุด เราขอแนะนำให้คุณสมัครใช้งาน webhooks ของเรา</p><h2 data-block-id=\"863d3d45-0669-40f7-b51c-f9d602694be0\">ตั้งค่า Webhook URL ของคุณ</h2><p data-block-id=\"98241c76-6e0d-4e79-9470-1d60440bc8ae\"><strong>สำคัญ:</strong> คุณต้องมีสิทธิ์เข้าถึงระดับ <code>Developer</code> เพื่อทำการตั้งค่า</p><p data-block-id=\"98241c76-6e0d-4e79-9470-1d60440bc8ae\">ทำตามคำแนะนำต่อไปนี้เพื่อเริ่มตั้งค่า webhook URL ของคุณ:</p><ol data-block-id=\"2394da81-f8ea-48a3-a732-ecfb59ad4afd\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"4dc6629e-21e4-4e4e-b0a0-397138b4d103\"><p data-block-id=\"a90efd07-2694-4d9c-b788-c7acca47e724\">เข้าสู่ระบบ Xendit Dashboard ของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"566c6980-6c91-4691-81ff-6ec1e70ceb49\"><p data-block-id=\"52609f8f-1f58-4e56-8523-e94c0fa0c7eb\">เปิด <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#webhooks\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Webhook Settings</strong></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ed67b9c2-3c6d-44b5-8606-172514301f85\"><p data-block-id=\"5bdff958-f47c-4b8d-b67a-21cf8a809c67\">กำหนดค่า <strong>URL ในแต่ละ webhook event</strong> ที่คุณต้องการสมัครใช้งาน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"39363386-69ef-48f5-ad6b-d4c3e8afd745\"><p data-block-id=\"056e4ed7-24d1-4a5f-a2de-6b8eb5911b44\">คลิก <strong>Test and Save</strong> เพื่อรับ test webhooks</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"73c6a165-cf78-4dbe-b0c4-2a161011bee1\">สำหรับข้อมูลเพิ่มเติมเกี่ยวกับ webhook events ต่างๆ ที่คุณสามารถสมัครใช้งานได้ โปรดดูหน้าการผสานรวมผลิตภัณฑ์ Payout ที่เกี่ยวข้องของคุณ</p><h3 data-block-id=\"a28b1831-ed44-4f55-b125-7047e14e55ff\">Payouts and Payout Links</h3><p data-block-id=\"e5395fa7-7a18-4100-97f2-bdf4d379c69c\"><img data-block-id=\"6d70ee74-22db-4b8f-b642-b56a04482c10\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(104).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"0b976c01-dc8d-40c3-9974-319906ba3fd2\">Cross-Border Payouts</h3><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"55a629d3-cad8-48d8-9766-bb5522e701ab\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"acf0fe21-b9de-44f1-a3b9-46e66263914c\">ข้อควรทราบที่สำคัญ</p></div><p data-block-id=\"44cca3e6-432a-4cf8-9a29-7cbf5aeddb9e\">แสดงเฉพาะเมื่อคุณลงทะเบียนเป็นนิติบุคคลที่ได้รับใบอนุญาตการโอนเงิน (remittance-licensed entity) ใน Xendit</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"c3034113-8c45-43a5-afbb-4b8d1cc6fbf2\"><img data-block-id=\"19e9f308-bafd-422c-8fdf-9f3e0b0a354c\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(106).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"2b8b4329-7609-4801-859e-b52643cdbafa\"></p>","SeoTitle":"ตั้งค่า webhook","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Configurar webhooks","Slug":"payouts-set-up-webhooks","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"58140471-fa0d-4d9a-a6d3-078d69246584\">Aprenda cómo puede recibir notificaciones de cualquier cambio de estado de sus Payouts en tiempo real. Para la mejor experiencia de Payout, le recomendamos encarecidamente que se suscriba a nuestros webhooks.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"863d3d45-0669-40f7-b51c-f9d602694be0\">Configure su URL de Webhook</h2><p data-block-id=\"98241c76-6e0d-4e79-9470-1d60440bc8ae\"><strong>Importante:</strong> Usted necesita acceso de <code>Developer</code> para configurar</p><p data-block-id=\"98241c76-6e0d-4e79-9470-1d60440bc8ae\">Siga las siguientes instrucciones para comenzar a configurar su URL de webhook:</p><ol data-block-id=\"2394da81-f8ea-48a3-a732-ecfb59ad4afd\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"4dc6629e-21e4-4e4e-b0a0-397138b4d103\"><p data-block-id=\"a90efd07-2694-4d9c-b788-c7acca47e724\">Inicie sesión en su Xendit Dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"566c6980-6c91-4691-81ff-6ec1e70ceb49\"><p data-block-id=\"52609f8f-1f58-4e56-8523-e94c0fa0c7eb\">Abra la <a href=\"https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#webhooks\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Configuración de Webhook</strong></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ed67b9c2-3c6d-44b5-8606-172514301f85\"><p data-block-id=\"5bdff958-f47c-4b8d-b67a-21cf8a809c67\">Configure su <strong>URL en cada evento de webhook</strong> al que desea suscribirse</p></li><li data-block-id=\"39363386-69ef-48f5-ad6b-d4c3e8afd745\"><p data-block-id=\"056e4ed7-24d1-4a5f-a2de-6b8eb5911b44\">Haga clic en <strong>Probar y Guardar</strong> para recibir webhooks de prueba</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"73c6a165-cf78-4dbe-b0c4-2a161011bee1\">Para obtener más información sobre los diferentes eventos de webhook a los que puede suscribirse, consulte la página de integración del producto Payout correspondiente.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"a28b1831-ed44-4f55-b125-7047e14e55ff\">Payouts y Payout Links</h3><p data-block-id=\"e5395fa7-7a18-4100-97f2-bdf4d379c69c\"><img data-block-id=\"6d70ee74-22db-4b8f-b642-b56a04482c10\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(104).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"0b976c01-dc8d-40c3-9974-319906ba3fd2\">Cross-Border Payouts</h3><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"55a629d3-cad8-48d8-9766-bb5522e701ab\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"acf0fe21-b9de-44f1-a3b9-46e66263914c\">Nota Importante</p></div><p data-block-id=\"44cca3e6-432a-4cf8-9a29-7cbf5aeddb9e\">Solo se muestra cuando usted está registrado como una entidad con licencia de remesas en Xendit</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"c3034113-8c45-43a5-afbb-4b8d1cc6fbf2\"><img data-block-id=\"19e9f308-bafd-422c-8fdf-9f3e0b0a354c\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(106).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"2b8b4329-7609-4801-859e-b52643cdbafa\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Configurar webhooks","Description":null}]